# Landing Page Copy

Read the landing page outline (`plan.md`), market analysis, and design brief. Write conversion-optimized copy for every section of the landing page. The copy document is the single source of truth for all text content during implementation.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write output to: {{task.changePath}}/copy.md

This step writes copy only. Do NOT create code, modify `plan.md`, or build anything.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

